OL,7,FAn advertorial from a British vape
OL,8,Findustry body has been banned for
OL,9,Fpromoting unlicensed e-cigarettes in a
OL,10,Fnewspaper.
OL,12,FThe ad from the Independent British
OL,13,FVape Trade Association (IBVTA), seen
OL,14,Fin the East Lothian Courier on October
OL,15,F26, featured the headline: "Let's
OL,16,Fclear the smoke of confusion: Vaping
OL,17,Fsaves smokers' lives."
