OL,7,FThe article went on: "A constant
OL,8,Fstream of negative headlines is
OL,9,Feroding the public's understanding of
OL,10,Fvaping's benefits, particularly among
OL,11,Fsmokers", and: "The IBVTA is now
OL,12,Fseeking to challenge some of the
OL,13,Fmisinformation we've seen over recent
OL,14,Fmonths and to educate smokers about
OL,15,Fthe benefits of vaping."
