OL,3,CVape industry advertorial banned for
OL,4,Cpromoting unlicensed devices in
OL,5,Cnewspaper
OL,7,FIt claimed that single-use vapes, due
OL,8,Fto their "user-friendly nature",
OL,9,Fplayed a crucial role in the initial
OL,10,Ftransition away from tobacco, with 53%
OL,11,Fof regular smokers and 61% of recent
OL,12,Fex-smokers using single-use devices.
OL,14,FA further paragraph said vaping,
OL,15,Fparticularly when using flavoured
OL,16,Fdevices, was "pivotal in achieving the
OL,17,FScottish Government's smoke-free
OL,18,Fambitions".
