OL,3,CVape industry advertorial banned for
OL,4,Cpromoting unlicensed devices in
OL,5,Cnewspaper
OL,7,FThe Advertising Standards Authority
OL,8,F(ASA) investigated whether the ad
OL,9,Fbreached rules by promoting
OL,10,Funlicensed, nicotine-containing e-
OL,11,Fcigarettes and their components in a
OL,12,Fnewspaper.
OL,14,FThe IBVTA said the ad presented
OL,15,Ffactual information about vaping and
OL,16,Fpresented findings from a piece of
OL,17,Fresearch about consumers' views on
OL,18,Fvaping.
