OL,4,Cpromoting unlicensed devices in
OL,5,Cnewspaper
OL,7,FThey said the ad was published during
OL,8,Fa time of "public misunderstanding of
OL,9,Fvaping harms, including that vaping
OL,10,Fwas more harmful than smoking".
OL,12,FThe ASA said the ad was published in a
OL,13,Flocal Scottish newspaper in response
OL,14,Fto the Scottish Government's proposal
OL,15,Fto ban the sale of disposable vapes by
OL,16,F2025.
