OL,5,Cnewspaper
OL,7,FThe regulator noted the ad did not
OL,8,Frefer to a specific brand of vape or
OL,9,Fvaping product, and therefore did not
OL,10,Fdirectly promote nicotine-containing e-
OL,11,Fcigarettes.
OL,13,FBut it said the ad's claims around the
OL,14,Fbenefits of single-use vapes had the
OL,15,Findirect effect of promoting them.
OL,17,FThe ad included a link to the IBVTA
OL,18,Fwebsite, which included a "Find a vape
OL,19,Fshop" feature, which the ASA said had
OL,20,Fthe further effect of indirectly
OL,21,Fpromoting unlicensed e-cigarettes.
OL,26,@zD@[OU{D@EO]
